Kalisz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalisz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 2021 trials in Omaha, Nebraska, Foster was the top seed coming out of the preliminaries, only to get chased down by both Kalisz and Litherland in the final.\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3145, \"end\": 3160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CHI_Health_Center_Omaha\", \"score\": 0.8972675400190081, \"rank\": 0.11369381060832665, \"text\": \"Omaha, Nebraska\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CHI_Health_Center_Omaha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CHI_Health_Center_Omaha\"}, {\"begin\": 3145, \"end\": 3160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CHI_Health_Center_Omaha\", \"score\": 0.8972675400190081, \"rank\": 0.11369381060832665, \"text\": \"Omaha, Nebraska\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CHI_Health_Center_Omaha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CHI_Health_Center_Omaha\"}, {\"begin\": 3162, \"end\": 3168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\", \"score\": 0.9999999996762199, \"rank\": 3.239326778817277e-10, \"text\": \"Foster\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\"}, {\"begin\": 3251, \"end\": 3257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalisz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.215658065273843e-15, \"text\": \"Kalisz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalisz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalisz\"}, {\"begin\": 3262, \"end\": 3272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Litherland\", \"score\": 0.999999999949523, \"rank\": 5.059560201436903e-11, \"text\": \"Litherland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Litherland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Litherland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The third-place finish cost Foster a trip to the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3316, \"end\": 3322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\", \"score\": 0.9999999996762199, \"rank\": 3.239326778817277e-10, \"text\": \"Foster\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the Americans went 1-2 at the Olympics, the missed opportunity hurt even more.\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kalisz closed to within a tenth of a second on the breaststroke leg, but the 30-year-old simply did not have enough in the tank to keep up with the younger Foster.\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3435, \"end\": 3441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalisz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.215658065273843e-15, \"text\": \"Kalisz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalisz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalisz\"}, {\"begin\": 3591, \"end\": 3597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\", \"score\": 0.9999999996762199, \"rank\": 3.239326778817277e-10, \"text\": \"Foster\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The winner pulled away on the freestyle, with Kalisz touching in 4:09.39.\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3645, \"end\": 3651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalisz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.215658065273843e-15, \"text\": \"Kalisz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalisz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalisz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Litherland faded at the end for a time of 4:12.34.\", \"from\": 3674, \"to\": 3724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3674, \"end\": 3684, \"title\": \"http://dbp